ot;If you've got a problem then petition&quot;<br><br>This has happened to me a couple of times now - and I am FED UP with newbies accusing anyone who helps em out of KS....but on the flip side they are always the ones begging for pp or buffs.<br><br>Perhaps I should just re-roll and watch these guys die whilst just laughing at em.<br><br>Grrr !!<br><br>Catrienna <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usolaneb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solaneb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 98<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/30/02 7:43:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1478.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Idiots</span><hr size=1> and if you didn't help you'd get<br><br>'why did you watch me die ?<br><br>just can't win LOL<br><br>i make a point of only help now if they yell,<br><br>i say while there battling want help ? if i get ignored i leave em, if they yell for help when it finall sinks in theat they aaren't gonna win tough, maybe next time they'll except the offer, just another of many lessons newbies need to learn,  <p><HTML><BODY><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td align="center"><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/05/16/flamingtext_com_1021571127_7055.gif" border=0 alt="Solaneb Benalos on FV" width="274" height="58"></a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=122558">My Gear</a><br>Peace and Tranquility are left in my wake<br> </tr></table></BODY></HTML></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ucobra102.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cobra102<